1. *Nazvaću* te ujutru. (I will *call* you in the morning.)
2. *Nazvala* sam te pre nekoliko minuta, ali nisi se javio. (I *called* you a few minutes ago, but you didn't answer.)
3. Da li ćete *nazvati* vašeg prijatelja da ga pozovete na večeru? (Will you *call* your friend to invite him for dinner?)
4. Molim vas da *nazovete* ovaj broj ako vam treba pomoć. (Please *call* this number if you need help.)
5. On će me *nazvati* kada stigne na aerodrom. (He will *call* me when he arrives at the airport.)
6. Ja sam *nazvao* majstora da popravi klimu. (I *called* the repairman to fix the air conditioner.)
7. Kada me *nazoveš*, javi mi se na viberu. (When you *call* me, message me on Viber.)
8. Oni su *nazvali* svoj restoran po dedi. (They named their restaurant after their grandfather.)
9. *Nazvao* sam taksi da me odveze do stanice. (I *called* a taxi to take me to the station.)
10. Molim vas da me *nazovete* kada stignete na aerodrom. (Please *call* me when you arrive at the airport.)